An official of Kano State Road Traffic Agency KAROTA, Abdulrahmam Isiyaku Bayero has been crushed to death by a trailer driver. Spokesperson, Nigeria Police, Kano State Command, DSP Abdullahi Haruna confirmed the incident to Daily Post. He said the incident occurred yesterday evening at the Ring road Junction, Hotoro Quarters area of Kano metropolis, while the officer was on duty. Kiyawa said the trailer driver has been arrested and the deceased returned to his relatives for burial according to Islamic rights. This is coming a day after the police arrested a commercial car driver who also killed an official of Kano state road Traffic Agency KAROTA. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.